{{Infobox football biography | name =Jussi Aalto | image =Jussi Aalto 1.jpg | fullname = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1983|07|28|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Rauma, Finland|Rauma]], [[Finland]]<ref>http://www.veikkausliiga.com/ennatykset_index.htm {{webarchive |url=https://www.webcitation.org/5hX7vE8Xu?url=http://www.veikkausliiga.com/ennatykset_index.htm |date=14 June 2009 }}</ref> | height = {{height|m=1.83}} | currentclub = [[Palloseura Kemi Kings|PS Kemi]] | clubnumber = 10 | position = [[forward (association football)|Forward]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = 2004 | clubs1 = [[Pallo-Iirot]] | caps1 = 46 | goals1 = 25 | years2 = 2005–2006 | clubs2 = [[HJK Helsinki]] | caps2 = 19 | goals2 = 3 | years3 = 2005–2006 | clubs3 = → [[Klubi-04]] (loan)| caps3 = 9 | goals3 = 4 | years4 = 2007–2008 | clubs4 = [[FF Jaro]] | caps4 = 47 | goals4 = 11 | years5 = 2008 | clubs5 = → [[Jakobstads Bollklubb|JBK]] (loan) | caps5 = 1 | goals5 = 1 | years6 = 2009–2010 | clubs6 = [[Vaasan Palloseura]] | caps6 = 40 | goals6 = 8 | years7 = 2011–2012 | clubs7 = [[FF Jaro]] | caps7 = 50 | goals7 = 6 | years8 = 2013 | clubs8 = [[FC Haka]] | caps8 = 24 | goals8 = 15 | years9 = 2014 | clubs9 = [[Seinäjoen Jalkapallokerho|SJK]] | caps9 = 0 | goals9 = 0 | years10 = 2014 | clubs10 = → [[Kotkan Työväen Palloilijat|KTP]] (loan) | caps10 = 26 | goals10 = 25 | years11 = 2015 | clubs11 = [[Turun Palloseura|TPS]] | caps11 = 26 | goals11 = 11 | years12 = 2016 | clubs12 = [[Kotkan Työväen Palloilijat|KTP]] | caps12 = 26 | goals12 = 15 | years13 = 2017– | clubs13 = [[Palloseura Kemi Kings|PS Kemi]] | caps13 = 2 | goals13 = 1 | pcupdate = 22 April 2017 (UTC) | ntupdate = }}
'''Jussi Aalto''' (born 28 July 1983) is a [[Finland|Finnish]] footballer who represents [[Palloseura Kemi Kings|PS Kemi]].
==Career==
On 21 December 2015, [[Kotkan Työväen Palloilijat|KTP]] announced that they had signed Aalto for the [[2016 Ykkönen|2016 season]] in [[Ykkönen]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Jussi Aalto palaa Kotkaan – Oskari Kekkoselle sopimus edustusjoukkueeseen|url=http://www.fcktp.fi/fi/jussi-aalto-palaa-kotkaan-%E2%80%93-oskari-kekkoselle-sopimus-edustusjoukkueeseen|publisher=KTP|accessdate=1 September 2016|language=fi|date=21 December 2015}}</ref>
